popularPosts.title: Majorana 1: Microsoft's Quantum Computing Breakthrough!
popularPosts.text:
There‚Äôs been a major breakthrough in quantum computing!! Microsoft‚Äôs research has led to the creation of Majorana 1 - a chip that can perform incredibly complex calculations that would be impossible for even the largest classical computers‚Ä¶ and I was lucky enough to be one of the first people to see in person!! 

This chip operates in a new topological state of matter, using Majorana particles instead of electrons, allowing it to store up to a million qubits. To achieve this, the chip is housed in an incredibly advanced freezer that can cool it down to just 50 millikelvin, 10 times colder than interstellar space.

This compact, powerful quantum computer has the potential to revolutionize fields like AI and scientific research.
